                <li>Withdraw consent at any time where we rely on consent for processing your personal data.</li>
            </ul>
            <p>
                <strong>What are cookies?</strong><br>
                Cookies are small text files placed on your computer to collect standard Internet log information and visitor behavior information.
            </p>
            <p>
                <strong>How do we use cookies?</strong><br>
